Package: ospsuite.reportingframework
Type: Package
Title: Provides a framework for report generation with the ospsuite
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Open-Systems-Pharmacology Community",
             role = "cph"),
      person(given = "Katrin",
             family = "Coboeken",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "katrin.coboeken@bayer.com"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <katrin.coboeken@bayer.com>
Description: This package uses the EsqlabsR package to set up simulations and scenerios.
    It provides functions to generate default graphics and tables.
    This figures are included in .Rmd files which are then merged 
    to the selected output format e.g. a "Report.docx".
